longBusinessSummary: Viratech Corp., through its subsidiary, Cambridge Golf LLC, operates as a sports lifestyle company. It designs and manufactures various nutritional products, sporting goods, and accessories to the sports, nutrition, and golf markets. The company was founded in 2006 and is based in San Diego, California.
